&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a part time Cashier/Reception Supervisor to join our friendly team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated individual to take responsibility for the supervision of the Inpatient and Outpatient reception teams and the Cashier role for the Inpatient team at Laureate House.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The reception team cover front of house Inpatient reception and telephone responsibilities as well as a number of other administration tasks and the Outpatient Reception team cover any clinics/appointments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone with excellent organisational skills to support our Reception teams as well as provide administration duties and the overseeing of the Cashier Office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hayley Grey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Admin Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tel: 0161 271 0750&lt;/p&gt;
